Hari Rhodes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hari_Rhodes 0 Hari Rhodes (April 10, 1932 – January 15, 1992) was an American author and actor whose career spanned three decades beginning around 1960. He was sometimes billed as Harry Rhodes and appeared in sixty-six films or television programs, such as ABC's 1963 TV medical drama series about psychiatry Breaking Point.
